modName: Windwood Redoubt - Home for bad guys
summary: An open ended wilderness player home full of chests/shelves for you to do with what you want. Built like a wooden bandit fortress. Includes a small cabin with a bed and cooking stone. Basic to do with what you like. Great for: Vampires/Forsworn/Bandits/Psychopaths - because there\'s a road right next to the fortress.
descriptionHtml:
An open ended wilderness player home full of chests/shelves for you to do with what you want. Built like a wooden bandit fortress. Includes a small cabin with a bed and cooking stone. Basic to do with what you like. Great for: Vampires/Forsworn/Bandits/Psychopaths - because there\'s a road right next to the fortress.

Eventually I\'ll add more customized versions, but right now this mod is for people who want to customize on their own. It works great with custom camping mods such as Portable Campsite - where you can set traps and tents and bandit-esque clutter wherever you want it.

This mod got a video review :)
See the videos section.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Check out my other player home mods: 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16143]Fire Dancer Retreat[/url] a mansion/manor in the reach with lots of features.

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16604]Cuilalie Haven[/url] a scenic elven designed player home for the rangers/wood elves who like to be out in nature. Built like a tree house and surrounded by a trellis and the nature around you. 

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17341]Caethspell Caverns[/url] a cave home for the druid nature/animal lover players. Includes a small indoor farm with livestock and crops - waterfall and pool, beautiful decor and scenery
author: Cynster
